oofem.out
2D notched beam, transport, midspan notch deleted via dual-edge midpoint test
TransientTransport nsteps 1 deltat 1 alpha 1. rtolf 1e-6 nmodules 1
errorcheck
domain 2dMassLatticeTransport
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all
ncrosssect 0 nmat 1 nbc 0 nic 0 nltf 1 nset 0
latticetransmat 1 d 1.e-9 k 1.e-13 vis 1.e-9 thetas 0.0924 thetar 0. ctor 0.001
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
